{"tid":121634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸塌樓多，民眾紛紛廢墟撿鋼變賣","createTime":"2017-02-15T11:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T01:34:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a30098198e5ab3785ff8afedee3d46d5afcaf5","tid":121634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/sketch-1487154661572.png?resize=1024%2C576\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fsketch-1487154661572.png%3Fresize%3D1024%252C576&h=d5911ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=6578#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D6578%23&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f43e1327\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=6578#</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸不時發生塌樓事故，加上正常的舊區拆卸，令社會上廢墟處處，但有不少低下層民眾卻從中發現了商機，紛紛到廢墟中撿拾鋼材變賣，造成社會問題。<br />\n<br />\n陸媒指，大部分「淘鋼者」都是貧窮老人，他們一天最多能抬2、30斤鋼去賣，能賺到數十元人民幣一日。<br />\n<br />\n由於拾鋼的都是老人，加上廢墟環境惡劣，容易跌倒引致嚴重受傷，對社會造成負擔，因此不少人都呼籲老人停止拾荒活動。"},{"pid":"252421233963152d6641ad08d86971583cea3733","tid":121634,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:41:59.000Z","msg":"分分鐘假鋼，執到都無用"},{"pid":"e7ca6168238d2be0770709699dbc4a199f0825d8","tid":121634,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00c8a4e93758ebe9a7aba40229b6faffb41737a","tid":121634,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分分鐘假鋼，執到都無用</blockquote><br />\n社會問題<br />\n<br />\n行乜1鬼資本主義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大鑊飯咪好羅"},{"pid":"a361b929f9c0fd1a79e662400795780914b2011f","tid":121634,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分分鐘假